# PostgreSQL Performance Benchmarking using Patent Dataset

## Overview

This project benchmarks PostgreSQL performance using a **9.45 million record Patent Dataset**.

The benchmark evaluates:

- Bulk Data Loading Performance
- LOGGED vs UNLOGGED Tables
- Partitioned Tables
- Query Performance
- Storage Usage
- Index Creation Strategies
- EXPLAIN ANALYZE Results

